(851, 1, '2019-01-13 04:45:43', '2019-01-13 04:45:43', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>About Our Service</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How do I get started?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please open an account for you and mention your delivery address, then proceed with your order. Having an account is always advantageous! Members get special discounts and cash back on every purchase!<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Where does the produce in the B&amp;B Organic come from?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We procure from different organic farms in India<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Is everything organic and certified?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can trust that 100% of the produce arriving to your home is organic. All our farms are certified as organic or at least they would have applied for organic certification, inorder to do the procurement from the farm. The core aim of our farms are to provide 100% organic products to customers and a rich biodiversity to every creatures in the environment<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Is your produce GMO-free?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes. Growing GMO-free is a very important component of organic certification<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What is B&amp;B Organics membership?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>B&amp;B organics has 3 types of membership: Silver, gold &amp; Platinum<br>Silver - 0 to 24999 Points. Get 0.25% cashback to your B&amp;B Wallet on every purchase<br>Gold - 25000 - 49999 Points. Get 0.5% cashback to your B&amp;B Wallet on every purchase<br>Platinum - 50000 + Points. Get 0.75% cashback to your B&amp;B Wallet on every purchase<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What is B&amp;B Organics wallet?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All cash that you gained during your purchase is stored in B&amp;B organics wallet. This cash can be used during your next purchase<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How is my order processed?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The following actions take place after you place your order:<br>1. You will get a notification through email of the confirmed order<br>2. The B&amp;B organics packing team gets notified of the order. The packing team prepares and dispatch the order<br>3. After the order gets dispatched, customer will receive an email with a tracking ID to track the product<br>Throughout the above stages, our order inspection team continuously monitors the process so that you get the desired product within the time committed to you. In case the order cannot be processed for any reason whatsoever, the same will be informed to you at the earliest<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>How will I know if any item in my order is unavailable?</li><li>We try to make sure the inventory at the store is always up do date. However, in case an item you ordered is unavailable, our order fulfilment team will notify you of the same immediately<br></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Free Shipping</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How does B&amp;B Organics shipping service work?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>B&amp;B Organics has tie-up with different shipping companies for delivery. Each shipping company offers different types of pricing and delivery style like shipping directly at home or picking up at their office. Customers can select it based on the pricing and comfortability<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How can I get very cheap shipping cost?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Higher the quantity, lesser the shipping cost. Therefore, we suggest ordering more to get less shipping cost. Further, we offer free shipping for orders above certain quantity. Please check offers page to know the quantity<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Delivery</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How does B&amp;B Organic\'s delivery service work?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We bring groceries from Monday to Saturday. B&amp;B organics direct delivery is applicable only in Trichy. For other cities, the delivery is done by the courier companies that you select while placing the order<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I did not receive my scheduled delivery. What do I do?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you do not receive a delivery, please contact us so we can investigate and assist with the proper handling of charges to you<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What if I receive an item in my delivery that I am not satisfied with?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We do our best to properly pack items for the journey from our Store to your door. If you receive produce that is damaged, or find an item missing from your order, please Contact us immediately and we will make it right. Quality produce and outstanding customer service are of utmost importance to us<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Would it be possible to have different city addresses under one account and still place orders for multiple cities?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, customers could place orders for multiple cities<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Would it be okay to add more than one delivery address in an account?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, customer could add many delivery addresses in your account. Nonetheless, remember that all items placed in a single order can only be delivered to one address. If you want different products delivered to different address place them as separate orders</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'FAQ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2019-01-21 01:43:34', '2019-01-21 01:43:34', '', 0, 'http://new.bnborganics.com/?page_id=851', 0, 'page', '', 0),
