stimonials][testimonial name=\"Raj Kapoor\" title=\"Mr\"]I have been using B&amp;B Organics products for more than a year and I do order on monthly basis. I highly recommend them whoever looking for certified and trusted natural farm fresh products.[/testimonial][/testimonials][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'Welcome', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-17 08:17:21', '2019-01-17 08:17:21', '', 25, 'http://new.bnborganics.com/2019/01/17/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(901, 1, '2019-01-21 01:09:28', '2019-01-21 01:09:28', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Currently, we deliver in bulk quantities to</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Organic grocery stores</li><li>Supermarkets</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please contact us for a quotation to order large quantities&nbsp;<strong>(e-mail: info@bnborganics.com)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you would like to sell organic products to us,please contact us.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that we buy only from certified organic farmers and the products that we buy undergo lab test also. If the lab test shows any pesticide residual then the products will be returned immediately.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Wholesale', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '838-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-21 01:09:28', '2019-01-21 01:09:28', '', 838, 'http://new.bnborganics.com/2019/01/21/838-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(900, 1, '2019-01-21 01:05:23', '2019-01-21 01:05:23', '', 'Here at B & B Organics, our motive is simple: providing farm fresh organic products to customers as soon as it is harvested from farms. B & B organics has aimed to provide easily accessible certified organic products to consumers and to provide secured income to farmers. Since children and women are highly vulnerable to the effects of chemically grown food and adulteration, eating organic food has become important nowadays. There is a myth that organic food is expensive but actually it is not – the price of organic foods is the real price of a product. Hence, don’t hesitate to pay the original price of a product to get a quality product. B & B Organics was founded in 2016 by Balaji, B.Tech (Horticulture). Dr. Balathandayuthabani, Ph.D in Environmental science (Sweden) and Dr. Rajasekaran, Ph.D in Soil Science (Germany) are his mentors. Balaji worked as a farm consultant during the years 2014-2015 and during that period, a doctor from Trichy requested him to supply organic foods. After the doctor started switching to organic foods, he requested Balaji to deliver organic foods to his friends as well. This is how B & B organics came into existence!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '859-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-21 01:05:23', '2019-01-21 01:05:23', '', 859, 'http://new.bnborganics.com/2019/01/21/859-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(902, 1, '2019-01-21 01:10:41', '2019-01-21 01:10:41', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here at B &amp; B Organics, our motive is simple: providing farm fresh organic products to customers as soon as it is harvested from farms. B &amp; B organics has aimed to provide easily accessible certified organic products to consumers and to provide secured income to farmers. Since children and women are highly vulnerable to the effects of chemically grown food and adulteration, eating organic food has become important nowadays. There is a myth that organic food is expensive but actually it is not – the price of organic foods is the real price of a product. Hence, don’t hesitate to pay the original price of a product to get a quality product. B &amp; B Organics was founded in 2016 by Balaji, B.Tech (Horticulture). Dr. Balathandayuthabani, Ph.D in Environmental science (Sweden) and Dr. Rajasekaran, Ph.D in Soil Science (Germany) are his mentors. Balaji worked as a farm consultant during the years 2014-2015 and during that period, a doctor from Trichy requested him to supply organic foods. After the doctor started switching to organic foods, he requested Balaji to deliver organic foods to his friends as well. This is how B &amp; B organics came into existence!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'ABOUT US', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '859-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-21 01:10:41', '2019-01-21 01:10:41', '', 859, 'http://new.bnborganics.com/2019/01/21/859-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(903, 1, '2019-01-21 01:11:23', '2019-01-21 01:11:23', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here at B &amp; B Organics, our motive is simple: providing farm fresh organic products to customers as soon as it is harvested from farms. B &amp; B organics has aimed to provide easily accessible certified organic products to consumers and to provide secured income to farmers. Since children and women are highly vulnerable to the effects of chemically grown food and adulteration, eating organic food has become important nowadays. There is a myth that organic food is expensive but actually it is not – the price of organic foods is the real price of a product. Hence, don’t hesitate to pay the original price of a product to get a quality product. B &amp; B Organics was founded in 2016 by Balaji, B.Tech (Horticulture). Dr. Balathandayuthabani, Ph.D in Environmental science (Sweden) and Dr. Rajasekaran, Ph.D in Soil Science (Germany) are his mentors. Balaji worked as a farm consultant during the years 2014-2015 and during that period, a doctor from Trichy requested him to supply organic foods. After the doctor started switching to organic foods, he requested Balaji to deliver organic foods to his friends as well. This is how B &amp; B organics came into existence!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '859-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-21 01:11:23', '2019-01-21 01:11:23', '', 859, 'http://new.bnborganics.com/2019/01/21/859-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
