(923, 1, '2019-01-21 01:45:23', '2019-01-21 01:45:23', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Terms</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In case you found any delivered product defective/damaged/not satisfied, you can report to B&amp;B Organics. We will not take back the damaged products, but we will return the money (5 to 7 working days to do the refund) or we will reduce the concerning amount in the next order.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This document is an electronic record in terms of Information Technology Act, 2000 ( IT act) and rules there under as applicable and the amended provisions pertaining to electronic records in various statutes as amended by the IT act. This electronic record is generated by a computer system and does not require any physical or digital signatures.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This document is published in accordance with the provisions of Rule 3 (1) of the Information Technology (Intermediaries guidelines) Rules, 2011 that require publishing the rules and regulations, privacy policy and Terms of Use for access or usage of concerned website.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to the www.bnborganics.com website (the Site). The site is operated by B&amp;B organics having address as shown at the end of the page. Both www.bnborganics.com and B&amp;B Organics are referred to as , also referred to as we, us in this document. This site provides services to you subject to the notices, terms, and conditions set forth in this agreement (the Agreement). In addition, when you use any of our services (e.g., Customer Reviews), you will be subject to the rules, guidelines, policies, terms, and conditions applicable to such service, and they are incorporated into this Agreement by this reference. We reserve the right to change this Site and these terms and conditions at any time.&nbsp;<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -