eading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In addition to any other legal or equitable remedies, we may, without prior notice to you, immediately terminate the Agreement or revoke any or all of your rights granted under this Agreement. Upon any termination of this Agreement, you shall immediately cease all access to and use of the Site and we shall, in addition to any other legal or equitable remedies, immediately revoke all password(s) and account identification issued to you and deny your access to and use of this Site in whole or in part. Any termination of this Agreement shall not affect the respective rights and obligations (including without limitation, payment obligations) of the parties arising before the date of termination.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>International Access<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This Site may be accessed from countries other than India. Any such references do not imply that such products will be made available outside India. If you access and use this Site outside India; you are responsible for complying with your local laws and regulations. At present www.bnborganics.com caters only to Indian market.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Typographical/ Inadvertant Errors<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the event a product/ food item is listed with incorrect information due to typographical error or Inadvertent errors in the photographs , description etc, we shall have the right to correct the same during any point without notice. We will not be liable for the losses caused to the customers because of the errors. But B&amp;B Organics will ensure that to the extent possible, correct information is provided.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Links</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This site may contain links to other sites on the Internet that are owned and operated by third parties. You acknowledge that we are not responsible for the operation of or content located on or through any such site.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Applicable Law</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This site is created in Bangalore but controlled by us in Tiruchirapalli, Tamil Nadu India. As such, the laws of the State of Tamil Nadu will govern these disclaimers, terms, and conditions, without giving effect to any principles of conflicts of laws.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Severability</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If any these provisions shall be deemed invalid, void, or for any reason unenforceable, that condition shall be deemed several and shall not affect the validity and enforceability of any remaining provision.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Copyright/ Trademark Information<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Copyright Â© 2016, B&amp;B Organics. All rights reserved. All trademarks, logos and service marks (Marks) displayed on the Site are our property or the property of other third parties. You are not permitted to use these Marks without our prior written consent or the consent of such third party which may own the Marks.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Return/ Replacement Policy and Cancellation</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In case you found any delivered product defective/damaged/not satisfied, you can report to B&amp;B Organics. We will not take back the damaged products, but we will return the money or we will reduce the concerning amount in the next order.&nbsp;<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If the delivery is not executed during first attempt due to incorrect or insufficient address, recipient not at home, address found locked or refusal to accept, the customer shall still be charged for the order. No refunds would be entertained for such items. But we will coordinate with the customer / shipping partner to complete the delivery.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that cancellations have to be made before shipping. For cancelling your order, you will have to use My account page. In case if we receive a cancellation notice and till that time the order has already been processed by us, the order cannot be cancelled. B&amp;B organics has complete right to decide whether an order has been processed or not. The customer agrees not to dispute the decision made by B&amp;B Organics and accept B&amp;B Organics decision regarding the cancellation.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Contact address</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Should you have any questions, concerns or suggestions, you may contact B&amp;B Organics by e-mail at info@bnborganics.com or at the following address:<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>B3 Ground floor, Praveensolai apartment, Lalgudi main road, No 1 toll gate, Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu 621216, India.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Terms & Conditions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '849-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-21 01:45:23', '2019-01-21 01:45:23', '', 849, 'http://new.bnborganics.com/2019/01/21/849-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
